Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.93,0:23:33.89,Default1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(261.714,283.714)\fn@方正超粗黑_GBK}好羞恥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.39,0:23:37.43,Default1,,0,0,0,,{\c&H434539&\pos(1155.429,265.429)\fn@方正超粗黑_GBK}小薰不能看這個
